docblock.long-description:
Callback or Closure can be passed as $default like this:

$a = 'John'

$value = CacheHelper::_('some cache', DAY_IN_SECONDS, function($key) use ($a){
     return "Hello $a";
});

Callback or Closure can be passed as $default like this:

$a = 'John'

$value = CacheHelper::getValue('some cache', function($key) use ($a){
     return "Hello $a";
}, DAY_IN_SECONDS);

